## Research Use

This implementation is provided to support research in quantum gravity and 
related fields. While the software is freely available, we encourage 
collaboration and proper attribution in research publications.

## Educational Use

This software is freely available for educational purposes. Educational 
institutions are encouraged to use and modify the code for teaching quantum 
gravity concepts, numerical methods, and scientific computing.

## Commercial Use

Commercial use is permitted under the MIT license terms. However, we request 
that commercial users consider contributing improvements back to the open 
source project to benefit the broader research community.